========================================
  PeopleFlow HR System - Local Setup
========================================

REQUIREMENTS:
  - Node.js installed (https://nodejs.org - download LTS version)
  - All devices must be on the SAME WiFi network

HOW TO START:
  1. Double-click START.bat
  2. A black window will open showing your server URL
  3. Example: http://192.168.1.5:3000
  4. Open that URL on any device connected to same WiFi

HOW TO SHARE WITH EMPLOYEES:
  1. Start the server (step above)
  2. Note the URL shown (e.g. http://192.168.1.5:3000)
  3. Share that URL with all employees
  4. They open it on their phones/laptops on same WiFi

IMPORTANT:
  - Keep the black window open while using PeopleFlow
  - All Supabase features (leaves, attendance, balance) 
    still need internet to sync across devices
  - To stop: press Ctrl+C in the black window

FILES:
  - index.html  : The PeopleFlow application
  - server.js   : Local web server
  - START.bat   : Double-click to start (Windows)
  - README.txt  : This file

========================================
